<P>__{(in thai)}
<D>__{... what?}
<C>__{chang}
<P>__{(in thai)}
<D>__{how could you let this happen?}
<C>__{choi yan lee}
<P>__{(in thai)}
<D>__{i didn't do anything.}
<C>__{chang}
<P>__{(in thai)}
<D>__{well now's your chance.}
<A>__{a long moment between them as choi yan lee fails to understand what chang is suggesting. chang stands back.}
<C>__{chang }
<P>__{(in thai)}
<D>__{do what thou will.}
